#: ../../../topics/api.rst:15
msgid ""
"The main entry point to the Scrapy API is the :class:`~scrapy.crawler."
"Crawler` object, which :ref:`components <topics-components>` can :ref:`get "
"for initialization <from-crawler>`. It provides access to all Scrapy core "
"components, and it is the only way for components to access them and hook "
"their functionality into Scrapy."
msgstr ""

